                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7614" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1196</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">3715 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蔚来与蔚能：亲如母子还是形同陌路？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">NIO and Weineng: As close as Mother and Son or Strangers?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">马悦，徐龙奥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东北师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">蔚来集团</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新能源汽车；控制权；合并范围；财务后果；2023百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New Energy Vehicles; Control Right; Scope of Consolidation; Financial Consequences</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近些年来，随着我国经济的发展和产业竞争的加剧，越来越多的企业通过投资、收购其他企业来增强自身实力，这也给合并财务报表的编制带来了新的要求与挑战。尤其在判断投资方对被投资方的控制权以及是否应将其纳入合并范围时，市场上的争议也越来越多。2022年6月28日，新能源汽车制造商蔚来遭遇做空，被推上风口浪尖，市场质疑声四起。本案例从蔚来被做空事件导入，回顾公司的发展历程以及其作为发起投资人与多方共同成立蔚能电池的原因，重点引出控制权的质疑焦点，引导学生思考蔚来是否对蔚能电池拥有实质控制权，如果把蔚能电池纳入合并报表会带来怎样的财务后果，并拓展思考如何规范企业控制权及合并范围的确认，如何加强管理部门对企业的监管，从而更好地保护投资者的利益。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the continuous development of the capital market of our country, more and more enterprises are investing in and acquiring other companies to increase their competitiveness, which has also brought challenges and requirements for the preparation of consolidated financial statements. Especially the control judging and the scope of consolidation, there are more and more controversies in the market. On June 28, 2022, the new energy vehicle manufacturer NIO was shorted and thrust into the limelight, with market scepticism abounding. This case starts with the shorting event of NIO, reviews the development of this company, and discusses whether NIO, as a main investor of Weineng, can control the company or not. The case guides students to consider how to judge the control right based on the principle of substance over form, and the impact on the consolidated financial statements. This case inspires students to discuss how to strengthen regulation and supervision when enterprises judge the control right and confirm the scope of consolidation so as to better protect the interests of investors.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务会计理论与实务》、《高级财务会计》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实质控制权；合并报表范围、长期股权投资的会计处理；合并报表抵消业务处理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
